# Phase 3.5.1: Worker Completion Plan

This phase migrates the final route dependency on the legacy `workerController.js` (`GET /api/v1/workers/admin/overview`) to the Clean Architecture worker module structure. It implements a clean domain use case and appropriate persistence repositories to calculate active/pending workers, total users, platform revenue, and live bookings, maintaining strict backward compatibility.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **No Legacy Deletions**: In accordance with the Phase 3.5 guidelines, no legacy files will be deleted or removed. The legacy controller `workerController.js` and routes file `worker.js` will remain intact as rollback fallbacks.
> **No Middleware / Service Modifications**: The `authMiddleware.js`, `validationMiddleware.js`, `reminderService.js`, `telegramService.js`, and `socketService.js` files will not be modified.

