## Rollback Plan

To revert Phase 3.5.1 and redirect the admin overview route back to the legacy controller:
```bash
git restore backend/src/modules/worker/interfaces/http/routes/workerRoutes.js
```
This restores the legacy controller import and route mapping. All newly added files can be left as-is on disk as they are not referenced elsewhere.
